	<h1 class="title">谁说跑酷很无聊，这款可以敲击手机背面玩</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1375/small/1375.jpg?1460641790" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐弢 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-09 09:32:33 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17226/medium/17226.jpg?1446797361" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


